      CV ; a human reviewer overrode the decision with the rationale
      "the AI scored 'poor fit' off the 'Analyst II' job title alone."
      Drop the bundle, open the dossier, see the oversight event bound
      by hash to the inference it reviewed. That is what closed-Gap-1
      through closed-Gap-4 looks like.
    </p>
